ns of the Deetz family return home to Winter River. Still haunted by Betelgeuse, Lydia's life is turned upside down when her teenage daughter, Astrid, accidentally opens the portal to the Afterlife.","genre_ids":[35,14,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.1536,"vote_count":2985,"poster_path":"/kKgQzkUCnQmeTPkyIwHly2t6ZFI.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-04","vote_average":6.944,"backdrop_path":"/kF8ljC7Y4p1UsmKBi2LxelZpqw.jpg","original_title":"Beetlejuice Beetlejuice","original_language":"en"},{"id":332872,"adult":false,"title":"Julieta","video":false,"overview":"The film spans 30 years in Julieta’s life from a nostalgic 1985 where everything seems hopeful, to 2015 where her life appears to be beyond repair and she is on the verge of madness.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5435,"vote_count":906,"poster_path":"/z4aErD1RQQ3alpu3PoUu408HEVc.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-08","vote_average":6.986,"backdrop_path":"/yG8iQi4gX0tjUBAvMNsliES3Czy.jpg","original_title":"Julieta","original_language":"es"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4022,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1151244,"adult":false,"title":"Vermiglio","video":false,"overview":"In the last days of the Second World War, a deserting soldier disrupts a tranquil and isolated mountain community. For one family, his arrival brings excitement and romance, but tragedy lies in wait.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.3691,"vote_count":304,"poster_path":"/aeCwM7c1Y1IAu3Oqqj5A2tSziWR.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-19","vote_average":7.061,"backdrop_path":"/fYepNPcgAYHQRMNZW95oOykLRgQ.jpg","original_title":"Vermiglio","original_language":"it"}],"similar_content":[{"id":3870,"adult":false,"title":"1900","video":false,"overview":"The epic tale of a class struggle in twentieth century Italy, as seen through the eyes of two childhood friends on opposing sides.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":1.9338,"vote_count":667,"poster_path":"/deWzfCC59tmtEQvKSmflDe14FvR.jpg","release_date":"1976-08-28","vote_average":7.798,"backdrop_path":"/x5948QrtMqvnf2OBP9ESpdmONQa.jpg","original_title":"Novecento","original_language":"it"},{"id":1039,"adult":false,"title":"The Inheritors","video":false,"overview":"In a small farming valley in Austria in the beginning of the 20th century a tyrannical farmer is found dead, and all the farmhands are relieved to be free of their tyrant. But the farmer was childless, so suddenly they all inherit the farm together. Now conflicts begin, as nobody is the boss and nobody has to obey.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3057,"vote_count":16,"poster_path":"/u6aCatHljw795MLscZwW1gYtOu2.jpg","release_date":"1998-06-19","vote_average":6.563,"backdrop_path":"/2xaiBXmpxDNurboSUsE5oZNX3Mi.jpg","original_title":"Die Siebtelbauern","original_language":"de"},{"id":1049,"adult":false,"title":"Sommersby","video":false,"overview":"Set in the South just after the US Civil War, Laurel Sommersby is just managing to work the farm without her husband, believed killed in battle. By all accounts, Jack Sommersby was not a pleasant man, thus when he suddenly returns, Laurel has mixed emotions. It appears that Jack has changed a great deal, leading some people to believe that this is not actually Jack but an imposter. Laurel herself is unsure, but willing to take the man into her home, and perhaps later into her heart.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648,10749],"popularity":3.819,"vote_count":418,"poster_path":"/tAgQKLv0GK97Tr0bvdI66oXlEVb.jpg","release_date":"1993-02-05","vote_average":6.341,"backdrop_path":"/jWAK7ONCE1Kski7SsAJvcNBQMyv.jpg","original_title":"Sommersby","original_language":"en"},{"id":1810,"adult":false,"title":"Viva Zapata!","video":false,"overview":"The story of Mexican revolutionary Emiliano Zapata, who led a rebellion against the corrupt, oppressive dictatorship of president Porfirio Díaz in the early 20th century.","genre_ids":[36,18,37],"popularity":0.8665,"vote_count":232,"poster_path":"/vfarxn9ddiaZpRDml8FGhB46Qrc.jpg","release_date":"1952-02-07","vote_average":6.884,"backdrop_path":"/7aX2mfTcQArKS9PufnngjexnaQY.jpg","original_title":"Viva Zapata!","original_language":"en"},{"id":11121,"adult":false,"title":"Tess","video":false,"overview":"A strong-willed peasant girl is sent by her father to the estate of some local aristocrats to capitalize on a rumor that their families are from the same line, but is left traumatised from her experiences.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.387,"vote_count":371,"poster_path":"/xejUFnoAVxzvU95o2jlzG2USmY.jpg","release_date":"1979-10-06","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/hEVAABU2c86MU42jlnGRM9FcCq5.jpg","original_title":"Tess","original_language":"en"},{"id":11139,"adult":false,"title":"Léolo","video":false,"overview":"The story of an imaginative boy who pretends he is the child of a sperm-laden Sicilian tomato upon which his mother accidentally fell.","genre_ids":[35,18,14],"popularity":0.7078,"vote_count":132,"poster_path":"/1HDTXmngKg6NHKGVnKADpxGPye5.jpg","release_date":"1992-09-16","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/7v4l2FnrpreaV19gY4xYiuPDPL2.jpg","original_title":"Léolo","original_language":"fr"},{"id":17227,"adult":false,"title":"Jacquou the Rebel","video":false,"overview":"In 1815, young Jacquou lives an idyllic peasant life with his parents in the Périgord region of France.  But one day, his childhood happiness is cruelly ended when his father is arrested, after a dispute with the arrogant Count de Nansac.  With both his parents dead, Jacquou is adopted by Bonal, a kind priest, under whose influence he grows into an assured, morally upright young man.  Now an adult, Jacquou has one desire.  To repay the Count de Nansac for the evil he once inflicted on his parents...","genre_ids":[12,18],"popularity":0.6385,"vote_count":146,"poster_path":"/jVLkOarUiKvFSLGSTQYGkdpwN2j.jpg","release_date":"2007-01-17","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/ldrPNqXFaK1Qful4L3Im4UbKP7f.jpg","original_title":"Jacquou le Croquant","original_language":"fr"},{"id":2012,"adult":false,"title":"Silent Light","video":false,"overview":"Johan and his family are Mennonites from the north of Mexico. Against the law of God and Man, Johan falls in love with another woman.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.3438,"vote_count":122,"poster_path":"/kniOoQky3GX9ljyzobwRUGFgQUT.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-02","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/gdQCvXF7TpBez8F4Ud6Chw94oJ3.jpg","original_title":"Stellet Licht","original_language":"de"},{"id":1993,"adult":false,"title":"Golden Door","video":false,"overview":"The story is set at the beginning of the 20th century in Sicily. Salvatore, a very poor farmer, and a widower, decides to emigrate to the US with all his family, including his old mother. Before they embark, they meet Lucy. She is supposed to be a British lady and wants to come back to the States. Lucy, or Luce as Salvatore calls her, for unknown reasons wants to marry someone before to arrive to Ellis Island in New York. Salvatore accepts the proposal. Once they arrive in Ellis Island they spend the quarantine period trying to pass the examinations to be admitted to the States. Tests are not so simple for poor farmers coming from Sicily. Their destiny is in the hands of the custom officers.","genre_ids":[36,18,10749],"popularity":3.0421,"vote_count":143,"poster_path":"/gjSK4pyVDt8Pwt9KpB8OtC246DC.jpg","release_date":"2006-09-22","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/rXjSUFn6muQvKq78IQpiKFew2t9.jpg","original_title":"Nuovomondo","original_language":"it"},{"id":11656,"adult":false,"title":"The Virgin Spring","video":false,"overview":"Devout Christians Töre and Märeta send their only daughter, the virginal Karin, and their foster daughter, the unrepentant Ingeri, to deliver candles to a distant church. On their way through the woods, the girls encounter a group of savage goat herders who brutally rape and murder Karin as Ingeri remains hidden. When the killers unwittingly seek refuge in the farmhouse of Töre and Märeta, Töre plots a fitting revenge.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":1.6999,"vote_count":662,"poster_path":"/z70YM3Y4pNYZATMhFMKonngaeMC.jpg","release_date":"1960-02-08","vote_average":7.844,"backdrop_path":"/pcBIabUibUmpOBggWckkjohXtiP.jpg","original_title":"Jungfrukällan","original_language":"sv"},{"id":917,"adult":false,"title":"Mother India","video":false,"overview":"A poverty-stricken woman raises her sons through many trials and tribulations. But no matter the struggles, always sticks to her own moral code.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.5346,"vote_count":101,"poster_path":"/AlfM9yLcK1rhv73iNbDiOU9vnnu.jpg","release_date":"1957-02-13","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/abU2NXnnwisg56vD1Lbg7Ui63GG.jpg","original_title":"मदर इण्डिया","original_language":"hi"},{"id":880,"adult":false,"title":"Antonia's Line","video":false,"overview":"After World War II, Antonia and her daughter, Danielle, go back to their Dutch hometown, where Antonia's late mother has bestowed a small farm upon her. There, Antonia settles down and joins a tightly-knit but unusual community. Those around her include quirky friend Crooked Finger, would-be suitor Bas and, eventually for Antonia, a granddaughter and great-granddaughter who help create a strong family of empowered women.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.7377,"vote_count":141,"poster_path":"/nUCVi6bBIL7LGC61nYaCqikAhIA.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-21","vote_average":6.883,"backdrop_path":"/sOkUBkwq21ZEThCX7wboY2Xl3m5.jpg","original_title":"Antonia","original_language":"nl"},{"id":688,"adult":false,"title":"The Bridges of Madison County","video":false,"overview":"Photographer Robert Kincaid wanders into the life of housewife Francesca Johnson for four days in the 1960s.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":3.0338,"vote_count":2321,"poster_path":"/aCBrhOQjhG397GLkEZ49zReQEKX.jpg","release_date":"1995-06-02","vote_average":7.704,"backdrop_path":"/4TnGcUsyd6ixuLWHaaEG5BGkAIp.jpg","original_title":"The Bridges of Madison County","original_language":"en"},{"id":836,"adult":false,"title":"Barren Lives","video":false,"overview":"In vivid images, the documentary-like story of a drover and his family in the northern badlands of Brazil during the drought. A family in the search of new hope and destiny.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3845,"vote_count":97,"poster_path":"/bBb4GiCZul2W6hhV8sbbnBnlhuE.jpg","release_date":"1963-08-22","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/3KBuZG9keFgKAbIRnMMn4MoOzo7.jpg","original_title":"Vidas Secas","original_language":"pt"},{"id":346,"adult":false,"title":"Seven Samurai","video":false,"overview":"A samurai answers a village's request for protection after he falls on hard times. The town needs protection from bandits, so the samurai gathers six others to help him teach the people how to defend themselves, and the villagers provide the soldiers with food.","genre_ids":[28,18],"popularity":7.7468,"vote_count":4120,"poster_path":"/lOMGc8bnSwQhS4XyE1S99uH8NXf.jpg","release_date":"1954-04-26","vote_average":8.451,"backdrop_path":"/qvZ91FwMq6O47VViAr8vZNQz3WI.jpg","original_title":"七人の侍","original_language":"ja"},{"id":5172,"adult":false,"title":"The Astronaut Farmer","video":false,"overview":"Texan Charles Farmer left the Air Force as a young man to save the family ranch when his dad died. Like most American ranchers, he owes his bank. Unlike most, he's an astrophysicist with a rocket in his barn - one he's built and wants to take into space. It's his dream. The FBI puts him under surveillance when he tries to buy rocket fuel, and the FAA stalls him when he files a flight plan – but Charles is undeterred.","genre_ids":[878,12,35,18],"popularity":1.2145,"vote_count":363,"poster_path":"/19uGc8wW3Ert1QvMYxvnReQkFMc.jpg","release_date":"2007-02-23","vote_average":6.255,"backdrop_path":"/l4hWbdxXompHvLIR0bl3m3WromI.jpg","original_title":"The Astronaut Farmer","original_language":"en"},{"id":10110,"adult":false,"title":"Empire of the Sun","video":false,"overview":"Jamie Graham, a privileged English boy, is living in Shanghai when the Japanese invade and force all foreigners into prison camps. Jamie is captured with an American sailor, who looks out for him while they are in the camp together. Even though he is separated from his parents and in a hostile environment, Jamie maintains his dignity and youthful spirit, providing a beacon of hope for the others held captive with him.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":2.8565,"vote_count":2071,"poster_path":"/gEaCzjwHoPgyQFcwHql7o5YLHAU.jpg","release_date":"1987-12-09","vote_average":7.502,"backdrop_path":"/xt7boIC763DdceVQIGJdnmKlDVu.jpg","original_title":"Empire of the Sun","original_language":"en"},{"id":10129,"adult":false,"title":"Autumn Milk","video":false,"overview":"With the death of her mother, eight-year-old Anna ends her childhood: From now on, she has to look after the nine-member family. Deprivation-rich years, which also find no end when Anna marries: Her husband Albert must be a soldier in the Second World War, and the pregnant Anna has to work hard in the farm and care sick relatives. Lonely and exposed to the harassment of the tyrannical mother-in-law, she waits for Albert, with no certainty that he will ever return.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3435,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/ifVFzDKcK0A1RFqUSywjfcXu38k.jpg","release_date":"1989-01-19","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/aX7ZrheufvDcmJzeDdTJ42vgrXA.jpg","original_title":"Herbstmilch","original_language":"de"},{"id":10268,"adult":false,"title":"You Are So Beautiful","video":false,"overview":"Aymé Pigrenet, a recently widowed farmer, is eager to find a new wife to help him run his farm. Desperate, he seeks the aid of a local matchmaker who suggest that he go to Romania to find a new wife. There he meets Elena.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.3021,"vote_count":179,"poster_path":"/8tn9qK9ulhBaI0SBQFaj0a2deBY.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-07","vote_average":6.377,"backdrop_path":"/gqbq8aGWB3lLHyIy6YFgDbnVK86.jpg","original_title":"Je vous trouve très beau","original_language":"fr"},{"id":12514,"adult":false,"title":"Die Scheinheiligen","video":false,"overview":"The starting point is the small (and real) town of Daxenbrunn, which has the misfortune of being located right on the highway to Salzburg. But Mayor Matthias and his friend and district administrator Dr. Seigis see the seemingly unfavorable geographical location as an opportunity to fill the empty coffers -- \"Hendl, mehr sog I ned\". A highway grill is supposed to redevelop the area, but in addition to the building permit, the land is also needed, and this is defended to the death by the old and stubborn farmer's wife Magdalena (great: Maria Singer) with weapons (!). Events come thick and fast when, almost simultaneously and independently of each other, art carver Johannes and asylum seeker Theophile turn up in the sleepy village and turn the local order upside down with their unflinching attitude.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.4442,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/9vnyI91JS2ytnNTHTUkyKfbiJi.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-01","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Die Scheinheiligen","original_language":"de"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt1284591","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q6570602","instagram_id":null,"mydramalist_id":"179671"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148492,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2010-09-22T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","release_dates":[{"note":"Venice Film Festival","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2008-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"US","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2009-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]}],"aggregate_credits":null,"original_network":null,"screenwriters":null,"based_on":null,"filming_location":"Tire","narrative_location":"Tire","review_score_rt":null,"review_score_mc":null,"box_office":null,"belongs_to_collection":{"id":663600,"name":"The Yusuf Trilogy","poster_path":"/30uWCgonPBCkI91Ias29oa8hnr7.jpg","backdrop_path":null},"collection_id":null,"wikidata_metadata":{"distributors":["Mozinet"]},"mood_tags":null,"trope_tags":null,"vibe_description":null,"ai_enriched_at":null,"ai_enrichment_version":0}}]]
